# RECURSIVE SCROLLS
 
![](https://i.imgur.com/9QZVh6y.png)
 
We create documents which describe how to replicate themselves.  The copies will also have replication information and so on. This creates an endlessly self-referential loop, depicted by an infinite chain of scrolls in scrolls.

